creator: NiftyBytes
descriptionHtml:
PractiScore is a complete scoring system supporting several types of competitions, including USPSA/IPSC, Steel Challenge, 3Gun, and IDPA matches.

Please email us any questions, support or enhancement requests and bug reports at support@practiscore.com

See our new PractiScore Competitor app. Search, download and analyze match results on your phone or tablet!

PractiScore has been extensively used for club matches as well as state and area matches with several hundred competitors.

Features include:
- FREE
- match can be configured, stages created and shooters registered on a tablet or phone without need for PC or connection to internet or any web site
- easy one finger scoring, simple and quick to use
- easy competitor registration with memory of shooters for less typing
- import shooter registrations from CSV file or from practiscore.com
- score summary view for paper backup
- instant stage and match results
- multiple squad support (any number of squads / shooters)
- WiFi syncing of scores and match definitions between devices
- instant e-mail of match results from the device
- instant posting of match results to practiscore.com
- export results to EzWS, WinMSS and RangeLog

You can contribute translations to other languages at https://practiscore.oneskyapp.com/admin/project/dashboard/project/74450
descriptionShort: Complete scoring system for IPSC/USPSA, Steel Challenge, 3gun, IDPA and other.

title: PractiScore

creator: NiftyBytes
descriptionHtml:
PractiScore is a complete scoring system supporting several types of competitions, including IPSC/USPSA, Steel Challenge, 3Gun, IDPA, ICORE, SASS/Cowboy, NRA/Bullseye, PRS and other matches.

The Bluetooth and Location permissions are required by Android system for syncing with other tablets over WiFi and to connect with Bluetooth-enabled timers.

Please email support@practiscore.com with questions, bug reports or enhancement requests.

PractiScore has been extensively used for club, state, area and national matches with several hundred competitors.

Features include:
- FREE
- match can be configured, stages created and shooters registered on a tablet or phone without need for PC or connection to internet or any web site
- easy one finger scoring, simple and quick to use
- easy competitor registration with memory of shooters for less typing
- option to import shooter registrations from CSV file or from practiscore.com website
- score summary view for paper backup
- instant stage and match results
- multiple squad support (any number of squads / shooters)
- WiFi syncing of scores and match definitions between devices
- instant e-mail of match results from the device
- instant posting of match results to practiscore.com
- export results to WinMSS and other formats

You can contribute translations to other languages at https://practiscore.oneskyapp.com/admin/project/dashboard/project/74450

title: PractiScore

creator: NiftyBytes
descriptionHtml:
The PractiScore app for android provides a complete scoring system supporting several types of competitions, including IPSC/USPSA, Steel Challenge, 3Gun, IDPA, ICORE, SASS/Cowboy, NRA/Bullseye, PRS and other matches.

It has been extensively used to run competitions at the club, state, area and national level with up to over a thousand of competitors.

Please email support@practiscore.com with questions, bug reports or enhancement requests.

The Bluetooth and Location permissions are required by the Android system for syncing with other tablets over WiFi and to connect with Bluetooth-enabled timers.

Features include:
- FREE
- match can be configured, stages created and shooters registered on a tablet or phone without need for PC or connection to internet or any web site
- easy one finger scoring, simple and quick to use
- easy competitor registration with memory of shooters for less typing
- option to import shooter registrations from CSV file or from the practiscore.com website
- score summary view for a paper backup
- instant stage and match results in offline
- multiple squad support (any number of squads / shooters)
- WiFi syncing of scores and match definitions between devices
- instant email of match results from the device
- instant posting of match results to practiscore.com for competitor viewing and verification
- export results to WinMSS and other formats

You can contribute translations to other languages at https://practiscore.oneskyapp.com/admin/project/dashboard/project/74450
